abstract: Pete Wells reviews Greenwich Village restaurant Chomp Chomp.
lead_paragraph: With the chef Simpson Wong’s ambitious hawker food menu, it’s like going from stall to stall without leaving your seat.

headline.main: Singapore Treats at Chomp Chomp in Greenwich Village
headline.print_headline: Treats Inspired by the Food Courts of Singapore
